    <overview>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The Leverhulme Trade Charities Trust awards bursaries, up to a total of £3,000, to students who have a parent, guardian or spouse that is employed as a commercial traveller, pharmacist or grocer. </p>
<p>Students can apply for up to £3,000. However, this is dependent upon financial need and funding available to the Trust year on year. </p>]]></Value>
